smjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104viw1665702683038.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/viw1665702683038.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/viw1665702683038.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"viw1665702683038\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                 \n Hash Message Authentication Codes (HMAC)\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Hash Message Authentication Codes (HMAC) use a hash function in combination with a secret key to create a message authentication code that can be used to verify the data integrity and authenticity of data. Only systems that also possess the secret key can detect changes to the message content.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"viw1665702683038__section_w1045ab1b5b1_w1046ab1b5_w1047ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"viw1665702683038__table_d3911e1_d3912e1_d3913e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Supported Hash Message Authentication Codes</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"viw1665702683038__table_d3911e1_d3912e1_d3913e1__entry__1\">Algorithm</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" id=\"viw1665702683038__table_d3911e1_d3912e1_d3913e1__entry__2\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"viw1665702683038__table_d3911e1_d3912e1_d3913e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">HMAC_MD5</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"viw1665702683038__table_d3911e1_d3912e1_d3913e1__entry__2\">HMAC using MD5 hash</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"viw1665702683038__table_d3911e1_d3912e1_d3913e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">HMAC_SHA1</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"viw1665702683038__table_d3911e1_d3912e1_d3913e1__entry__2\"> HMAC using SHA-1 hash</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"viw1665702683038__table_d3911e1_d3912e1_d3913e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">HMAC_SHA224</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"viw1665702683038__table_d3911e1_d3912e1_d3913e1__entry__2\">HMAC using SHA-2 (224 bits) hash</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"viw1665702683038__table_d3911e1_d3912e1_d3913e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">HMAC_SHA256</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"viw1665702683038__table_d3911e1_d3912e1_d3913e1__entry__2\"> HMAC using SHA-2 (256 bits) hash</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"viw1665702683038__table_d3911e1_d3912e1_d3913e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">HMAC_SHA384</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"viw1665702683038__table_d3911e1_d3912e1_d3913e1__entry__2\">HMAC using SHA-2 (384 bits) hash</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"viw1665702683038__table_d3911e1_d3912e1_d3913e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">HMAC_SHA512</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" headers=\"viw1665702683038__table_d3911e1_d3912e1_d3913e1__entry__2\"> HMAC using SHA-2 (512 bits) hash</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"viw1665702683038__section_qjz_jq1_4cc\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table frame-all\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"viw1665702683038__table_evy_ypg_q3c\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Related learning videos</span></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"/><col style=\"width:50%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"viw1665702683038__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__1\">Title</th>\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"viw1665702683038__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__2\">link</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"viw1665702683038__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__1\">Hash Message Authentication Codes (HMAC)</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"viw1665702683038__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"https://vimeo.com/1164385024\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"Watch or listen Hash Message Authentication Codes (HMAC) video\" class=\"image\" id=\"viw1665702683038__image_nvt_tfg_q3c\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/My_Video_Button.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/></a></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533040\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533040\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Hash Message Authentication Codes (HMAC) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 18, 2026 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Hash Message Authentication Codes (HMAC) Hash Message Authentication Codes (HMAC) use a hash function in combination with a secret key to create a message authentication code that can be used to verify the data integrity and authenticity of data. Only systems that also possess the secret key can detect changes to the message content. Table 1. Supported Hash Message Authentication Codes Algorithm Meaning HMAC_MD5 HMAC using MD5 hash HMAC_SHA1 HMAC using SHA-1 hash HMAC_SHA224 HMAC using SHA-2 (224 bits) hash HMAC_SHA256 HMAC using SHA-2 (256 bits) hash HMAC_SHA384 HMAC using SHA-2 (384 bits) hash HMAC_SHA512 HMAC using SHA-2 (512 bits) hash Table 2. Related learning videos Title link Hash Message Authentication Codes (HMAC) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}